title: Episode 212: Bathroom Tales (Feat. Aida Rodriguez and Chaunte Wayans)
itunes:title: Episode 212: Bathroom Tales (Feat. Aida Rodriguez and Chaunte Wayans)
description:
Comedians Aida Rodriguez and Chaunte Wayans join the ladies of Lip Service this week. The ladies cover a range of topics from having sex with strangers while on the road, dating people for a meal, leading people on, and much more. The ladies even have their own bathroom experiences that are quite the story.
